Bit Rate Stage.title: Opening Ceremonies
Bit Rate Stage.description: Welcome to another Ponyfest!!!

Bit Rate Stage.title: MC-Arch
Bit Rate Stage.description: All the way from the Netherlands with a heart full of Passion and Willpower, MC-Arch is happy to make Ponyfest completely rise up with Hiphop music to the fullest of volumes and joy! the Power of Brony hiphop is STILL HERE! And it’ll be shown through a heartfelt show full of Passion, heartwarming, and energetic mix of Rap/Electronic/Soul music! and is happy to be there and contribute to yet again to spreading the power of Music and connecting people together with it!

Bit Rate Stage.title: Pipetka
Bit Rate Stage.description: A variety of Dubstep, Drum and Bass, and EDM

Bit Rate Stage.title: Trey Husk
Bit Rate Stage.description: Trey Husk is a Music Producer and DJ based in Columbus, Ohio. He has been up and coming in the Brony and Furry fandoms, having various music releases on Ponies At Dawn, StarlingEDM, and Aural Alliance. Not to be confined to the online space, Trey has performed live at many fandom conventions nationwide, including AnthroCon, HarmonyCon, TrotCon, and many others. Prepare to get lost in the sound, with his catalog of uplifting dance and feel-good vibes.

Bit Rate Stage.title: Kakofonous A. Dischord
Bit Rate Stage.description: A DJ set of the hardcore techno music of the Pinkamena Party compilation scene. With over 10 years of music, we would love to share a PG-13 exploration of our groups' tunes with PVFM!

Bit Rate Stage.title: ∆•RYZ
Bit Rate Stage.description: Celebrating 13 years of PVFM and 10 years of ∆•RYZ, join us for an immersive earth-shattering experience of high-energy, melodic dance music.

Bit Rate Stage.title: Acid Applejack
Bit Rate Stage.panelists: Hard dance set for the fandom
Bit Rate Stage.description: Hard dance DJ set. Which means genres like hardstyle, uk/happy hardcore, frenchcore, maybe uptempo hardcore and maybe some 90s hardcore/happy hardcore

Bit Rate Stage.title: RezKue!
Bit Rate Stage.description: Tune in for an hour of heavy, melodic, and rowdy electronic music from RezKue! celebrating the 13th Anniversary of PVFM.

Bit Rate Stage.title: BlueIntellect
Bit Rate Stage.description: DJ

Bit Rate Stage.title: Thrack
Bit Rate Stage.description: Piratey music typically all acoustic

Bit Rate Stage.title: DoTheDaringDew
Bit Rate Stage.description: Simple acoustic guitar and mic setup with some potential pedals. Primarily, though, it's my acoustic guitar and my vocals.

Bit Rate Stage.title: Metajoker
Bit Rate Stage.description: An alt-rock/EDM blend of classic and new Metajoker tunes!

Bit Rate Stage.title: SCR4TCHK4T
Bit Rate Stage.description: Hyper Heaven! A playful mix that features all sorts of hyperpop and happy hardcore tracks that are sure to be enjoyed by everypony! ♡

Bit Rate Stage.title: Steryotype
Bit Rate Stage.description: Lofi Hip Hop + an assortment of remixes

Bit Rate Stage.title: pocketjawa
Bit Rate Stage.description: Happy Hardcore to close out the night

Bit Rate Stage.title: Closing Ceremonies
Bit Rate Stage.description: Thank you for all the fish
